name: jstask
description: Requires a natural number greater than 0 adn smaller than 10000 to be inputed. Will display for each number in the interval 1 to n (number typed in the input)  - foo bar if the number is divisible by 2 and 3 - foo if the number is divisible just by 2 - bar if the number is divisible just by 3 - and the iterration number in the other case.
